Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, little boy! That thing\NI asked you to do yesterday—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those limited edition figurines from\NAkiba and the yokan from Masuya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I already got them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well! Aren't you Mr. Competent?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, who would've thought\NMs. Hana was such a callous mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.88,0:00:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you wait... I'll\Nget back at you for this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.39,0:00:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge! Over here, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's another chilly day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we shop today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're not wearing\Nyour usual ribbon today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a make-over?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.07,0:00:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, I guess you could call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Well, I think that one\Nlooks good on you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, by the way, what's going on\Nwith that Christmas party?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Shu's idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's a go for tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're inviting people from our\Nclass, and we'll all be there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.67,0:01:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Today we're getting\Ngifts for the grab bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.97,0:01:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I came, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:41.73,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Mother"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The reservation for your company dinner\Nand all the schedule adjustments are done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me my next task!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, you took care of\Nthat quicker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth has gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your work has been\Nstellar the last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that you haven't\Nbeen a godsend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I'll have to add\Na generous tip to your paycheck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting paid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those who work must be compensated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rule of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've already made that\Nhotel reservation for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it will be fine,\Nentrusting her to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a mother, I don't know\Nif it's appropriate to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but go on and have as much fun\Nas high school kids should!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or the hotel room, needless to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do have one favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I work extra hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and that gives you some extra time\Ntomorrow on Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do you think you can\Ngo see Chitoge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep up this pace and work to death,\NI can open up some time for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you go or can't you? Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course it's a possibility, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I need to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey - wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It could be that I'm only\Nbutting in needlessly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Same as the other day - it's like\NI will end up hurting her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't leave things like this...\Nthat would be too cruel to poor Chitoge!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know if it'll fix things\Nbetween them if they meet up,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I want to do whatever\NI can for her, at least!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All the work I was supposed to do\Nthis month... It's all right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And judging by your\Nrecent tendencies,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,everything you might need\Nas gifts for your clients...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone out and purchased them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, you do amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've done everything that\NI possibly could. Ms. Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you now! Please go see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I won't be going. Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a matter of time,\Nyou've got that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, at least just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just give her this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I went out and bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a scarf inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please give it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not another one. Didn't I\Ntell you there was no need?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not really\Nup to you, is it, Ms. Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, you're overstepping!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're sticking your nose into other\Nfamilies' business way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana, don't you want to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not really as if I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see... Is that it, then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you never had the slightest interest\Nin Chitoge from the start, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you've opened up my schedule,\Nthen that's convenient for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is book\Nanother appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why, you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did get her something,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems I won't get a chance\Nto give it to her this year, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Ms. Hana... is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present. For Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've just been piling up\Nfor the last ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every single year, I get her one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then end up not being\Nable to give it to her, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana, did you just eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a chocolate cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you used to\Neat these as a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for real cigarettes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,once I became pregnant\Nwith Chitoge, I quit cold turkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What the...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... But I thought you didn't\Nhave any interest in Chitoge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot all about\NChitoge's ribbon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.84,0:06:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you always\Nforget how old she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'd never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the ribbon\NI gave her, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whaaaaat did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that girl's still wearing that cheap\Nribbon I gave her ten years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:07:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm sure she can find something\Nthat would become her more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As for her age, of course I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that... when I'm\Nwith her, I get so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that I start out by asking her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That will only backfire on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she an amazing girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I told you this before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the ability,\Nit's your duty to exercise it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is gifted with\Nmarvelous abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she put her mind to it, she could\Nfar surpass both Adelt and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but she's\Na beauty, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've raised her quite strictly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure I was far too strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it,\Nshe stopped calling me "Mom."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she must\Nreally hate me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you came up with the idea of\Nsending us to a hotel on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I thought\Nthat would make her happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:07:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This woman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, so that was it, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally see it now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... How dare you do such a thing to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong on the most basic level!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't hate you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's needed you all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was totally looking forward to\Nspending Christmas Eve with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, except\Nwhen she's with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she still calls you "Mom," you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, go see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to head\Nto the U.S. after this today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then... how much\Ntime do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours before\Nmy flight takes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, that's cutting it close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana, once you've finished\Ngetting ready for your trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,please wait at that five-star suite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll bring Chitoge to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}here I was, thinking Ms. Hana\Nwas a wizard at her job...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but other than that, she's\Nnothing but an airhead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess the apple doesn't\Nfall too far from the tree!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look outside! It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? It's a white Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet something wonderful's\Nin store for us this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Young Mistress, aren't you\Ncold standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, when will\NMaster Raku be arriving?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I'm sure he'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Mom! I want\Na ribbon just like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, you can have one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take good care of it, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder when things\Ngot like this between us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I used to be able to\Ntalk to her, just like that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it always going to be like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom and me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, what, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oooooooh! Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be with my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No time to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just come with me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up a second! This is so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At least tell me where!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To a five-star hotel suite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.93,DefaultTopLeft,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana Kirisaki\NThis is a boarding time change notification.\NAs the snow is predicted to become heavier, \Nthe charter flight you have reserved will be leaving earlier than scheduled.\NPlease be sure to be on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good, Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The heavy snow up north is\Ncausing a major traffic jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This car isn't going anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to bring it\Nback right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That hotel you mentioned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's the one Mom was\Ntalking about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I go with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana is waiting for you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you to see her, so just\Nshut your mouth and sit there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's there? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ms. Hana... Sure, she said a lot of\Nthings that could be taken the wrong way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I wouldn't blame you\Nif you didn't believe me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, she really,\Nreally cares about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way could I ever believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For once in your life,\Nwhy don't you just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She said her flight was\Nleaving early because of the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The airport, then! Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The snow is intensifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to miss this meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it will mean a loss of several\Nbillion yen for our company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna make...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please ditch that appointment, Ms. Hana!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, little boy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's enough, all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It made me happy to hear\Nhow Chitoge feels about me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but... I've got to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please give her my regards, will you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you go, blaming it\Non your work...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, you're\Njust scared, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A woman your age, what\Nare you doing running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.65,0:13:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important,\Nyour work, or her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to think\Nlong and hard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still love your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do... love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I never get to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and even when you're with me,\Nall you do is yell at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And even though you never\Neven look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I have no idea\Nwhat you're thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And did I mention that\NI'm terrified of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I still love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought,\Nthey're two of a kind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too cold for you to have\Na long heart-to-heart here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to head back to the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and deal with the aftermath\Nas best I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so you go on to the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and spend a relaxing Christmas\NEve with her, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to dial down\Nthe heroics, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you can make\Nan exception. For today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...as a "Merry Christmas," okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't given you your\NChristmas present, have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.87,0:16:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A new ribbon - I picked it out for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:17:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It does make me very happy to know\Nthat you treasure that ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you are a girl, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.93,0:17:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to go on\Ntreasuring this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since this one brings back\Nso many memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that will make that\Nboy very happy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.75,0:17:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy is the reason you started\Nwearing that ribbon, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, you and that boy spent\Na summer playing together, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and there was a girl\Nwearing a ribbon like that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in one of the picture books\Nyou adored at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that boy said to you, "I bet\Nthis ribbon would look good on you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you rushed over\Nto pester me for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:18:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go to him? Chitoge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was all thanks to that boy that\NI got to have this long talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's your boyfriend, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should go to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you sleep here,\Nyou'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid bean sprout...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Raku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd help me out\Nthis much, both in business and in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, to think that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be reunited like this with that little boy\Nwho played with Chitoge ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a strange\Ntwist of fate, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana, you were there,\Ntoo, ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.51,0:19:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I remember you very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Ms. Hana...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does this locket look\Nat all familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.02,0:20:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something about that\Ntime that I want to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't seem to recall it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can\Nhelp you with that. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come here for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.71,0:20:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... I hear you and Chitoge are just\Npretending to be dating, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hana... you knew all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not from the start, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should've told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I feel stupid for\Ngoing all-out to fake it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Faking it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I work extra hard, do you\Nthink you can go see Chitoge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.66,0:20:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm asking you now! Please go see her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really nothing\Nbut a sham, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are your feelings for that girl\Nreally nothing more than a sham?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then - please\Nlook after my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After Chitoge and I saw Ms. Hana off,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got a call from Shu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, they were\Nunder the impression
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that Chitoge and I had spent\Nthe night in a hotel suite,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and wanting to know what we'd\Nbeen up to, they interrogated us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though we did manage to\Nstraighten them out,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it ended up being\Na hell of a Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That locket...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the one that came out\Nin Chitoge's picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, till the next time I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.73,0:22:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many years will\Ngo by before we meet again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're heading over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Christmas party ended hours ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ruri, telling me the trains weren't\Nrunning... don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.46,0:23:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were really asleep till now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We really had our\Nhands full, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.71,0:23:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.72,0:23:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really am glad that\Nit was a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, that's okay,\Nno need for apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You use that present\Nyourself, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.60,0:24:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want it!
